messages.messageBody:
In my travels, I came across these two Personality Tests I thought you folks
might like. I personally find them even more entertaining than Meyers-Briggs.
(By the way...I am INFP...what are you?

The first tells you what Fellowship of the Ring character you most resemble.
http://www.vista-ray.com/~matt/lotr/
I am Frodo.

The second tells you what dead Russian composer you are most like.
http://www.angelfire.com/va/randomlyweird/russcomp.html
I am Nikolai Rimsky-Korsakov (and don't really know enough about dead Russian
composers to understand the significance.)

Kathryn Baptista
